E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Jim, I love you man, but since you've hit middle age, you've really lost something...
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Jim，我爱你，兄弟。但自从进入中年，你就少了点东西...

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You're gonna have to take charge of the chapter, man.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~必须由你来接管分会了，兄弟。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Another deal fucked up in Liberty City. Don't look so surprised, man. Adios.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~自由城又出了一桩砸了的买卖。不用惊讶，兄弟。再见。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~The cops are all over us, man. We've got to lose them.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~屁股后面全是条子，兄弟。我们要甩掉他们。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~The heroin my cousins sweated over in order to bring to this country
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我的兄弟们千辛万苦走私进来的海洛因，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~How'd you find out that H belonged to the Triads?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你怎么知道这批白粉是三合会的？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, man. We've got to lose this heat.
~z~Maybe he's stuck too much of that brown into his arm then.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~也可能是他打海洛因打疯了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Hey, man. Hey, hey, huh? What, what, what, what you looking for?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，老兄。嘿，嘿，哈？啥啥啥，你找啥？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~but this Jew prick. He fucked us over, man.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~但这个犹太混蛋，他整了我们，兄弟。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Hey, they don't need luck, we're looking out for them.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，他们不需要好运，有我们罩着呢。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You stay away from us, you hear?
~z~We got to get through it. Brothers for life, man. Lost forever. I'll see you soon.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们要挺过去。生死兄弟情，哥们。失落帮万岁。以后见。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You should take over as Chapter President, Johnny.
~z~Okay? Why don't you just suck 'em off while you're at it?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好吧？你怎么不直接给他们口一发？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You hear that, Brian? Looks like it's only Billy gonna let you blow him.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~听见了吗，Brian？看来肯让你口的人就只有Billy。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~hold hands, pray, and sing Kum Ba Yah.
~z~Nothing mellow about what you're about to walk into, brother. Watch out.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~接下来的事情很难让人放松，兄弟。当心点。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~What do you mean? Johnny and I were getting jumped. Why weren't you helping Billy?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你什么意思？Johnny和我被袭击了。你怎么没保护好Billy？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~but these aren't the type of dudes you say "fuck 'em" to.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~但这些人不是随随便便就能「去他妈的」的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Easy Jim, look who the fuck you're speaking to huh.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~注意点，Jim，你他妈怎么跟老大说话的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I'm calling the brothers. We got to talk about this shit.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~I'm calling the brothers. We got to talk about this shit.

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I'm too tired to start playing the blame game with you, Brian.
~z~What you guys do is your own business, man? You're both adults. Well, kinda.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你们做了什么是你们的事，老兄。你们都是成年人了。好吧，一定程度上是。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Giving it up to the slopes. It don't feel right.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~向那群猴子示弱，感觉不太对。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Jim, you're wrong, man. I know you're a good guy -
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Jim，你错了，兄弟。我知道你是好人，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You are here to sell us back our heroin.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你们想把我们的海洛因卖给我们。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Watch yourself, Johnny. We got more here.
~z~They're some heavily armed, pissed off motherfuckers,
~z~Billy, I've got Chad on the phone!
~z~Yeah, you're right we probably should all get into a circle,
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~对，有道理，我们应该围成一圈，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~There is - that H we stole - it belonged to the Chinese.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~的确有。我们偷来的白粉原本是中国人的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~After that shit Billy was saying, you think we'll still have a chapter?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Billy能说出那种话，你觉得我们的分部还能维系吗？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Thanks for that, Brian. Real helpful input.
~z~Johnny, you're wasting away, man. I think it's all the worrying you do. Why don't you hit the weights later?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，最近瘦了啊，兄弟。我看你就是每天想得太多了。待会儿你去举个铁吧？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I had to help myself, man. I mean, I can't be expected to...
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我得先保护好自己，兄弟。我是说，总不能指望我...

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Hey Brian. Johnny's not like that, man.
~z~I knew you were a rat, now he's gone, man.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我就知道你是叛徒，现在他没了，伙计。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I just don't trust those little yellow bastards.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我就是信不过这帮黄皮崽子。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I think a guy like you should be pleased.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你这样的人一定会很高兴的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Where the fuck were Billy and his little bitch during that shit storm?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~出事的时候Billy和他的狗腿子他妈在哪儿？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck are you talking about,
~z~Get lost before I put my foot in your face. OK buddy?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~再不滚蛋老子踩烂你的臭脸。懂，伙计？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Man, let's just get back to the bikes.
~z~Was that because I stuck it to Ashley?
~z~Look, man. Look, look, look. I been up for three days, man.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~听着，老兄。听着，听着，听着。我来这儿三天了，老兄。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Yeah but Jim says there's some problem.
~z~who killed a couple of Angels when they found out their shit was gone.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~知道货被偷了以后就杀了几个死亡天使祭天。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Jesus. That was heavy, man. Fuck it.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，实在太糟糕了，兄弟。妈的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Shut your God damn mouth, shut your mouth!
~z~I'm not the one with an authority problem, Johnny.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~平时质疑权威的人又不是我，Johnny。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~We need to take a hard look at things. Follow me back to the house.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们要好好调查一下了。跟我回会所。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Look we have a business opportunity here Johnny.
~z~That's bullshit. If you were looking out for us, where were you when me and Johhny had to fight our way outta there?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~放屁吧你。要是真在暗地保护，我和Johnny杀出重围的时候你在哪里？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~But you're the leader, so that's the way it goes.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~但你现在是老大，所以就这样吧。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Okay, Jim. I guess I got to take over as Chapter President now.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，Jim。看来我必须接任分会会长了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~We gonna be cool and do this thing?
~z~They saw him and they've been calling him...
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~被盯上以后，条子就一直打电话找他...

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Alright, Brian. I'd like to know what the fuck went down as well.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好的，Brian。我也想知道到底是怎么回事。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Dude, this feels weird. Let's get to the bikes.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~老兄，感觉不对劲。我们去车子那儿吧。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~that possession is nine tenths of the law -
~z~Foolish Americans! Your greed has ruined you yet again.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~傻逼美国佬！又被自己的贪婪害死了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Bill, yeah, he's fucked now. Thanks to you. I'm around the corner.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Bill，对，他现在完了，多亏了你啊。我就在路口那儿。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Now I'm thinking maybe we can strike up a deal with them.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~依我看，我们可以跟他们谈笔交易。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I think you knew more about the brown when we found it at the Deabeats pad and I think you know more now.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~在死妈天使的会所找到货的时候我就觉得你知道的很多，现在更是如此。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Brian here says he wants to suck your cock too, Jim.
~z~Shit, Billy. You're the fucking man. How bout you beat us brothers in a race just to prove it.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Billy。现在你最牛逼，要么跟哥几个飙车证明一下吧？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~We were watching your back, man. Looking out for you brothers. Doing more than you did for Billy.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们在保护你的后背，兄弟。暗地保护你们。做的可比你替Billy做的多多了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Well you don't have to do either, man.
~z~Okay, we gotta sort shit out. Tail me over to the house.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好了，我们要好好理一理。跟我回会所。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You have walked into a trap, fools!
~z~You must have fucked shit up, Johnny. Billy never wanted to make nice in the first place.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~都是你的错，Johnny。Billy一开始就没考虑过谈判。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~that offloading the heroin would be a good idea, alright!?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~立刻把海洛因脱手会是明智之举，懂吗！？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~In this country they seem to be the same thing,
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~在这个国家，两者似乎没有区别，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I'm just trying to explain to our friend here -
~z~We can't let the pigs take us, too. Come on.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~不能让条子把我们也抓进去。快逃。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You wanna fuck? Huh? I'm kinda crazy right now.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~想找事吗？啊？我现在可有点疯。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Fuck, man. Billy's gonna go away for good with those priors of his.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~操了，兄弟。有之前的案底在，Billy这次是回不来了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~prove you ain't been speaking to the law.
~z~I'm surprised Brian isn't here fighting alongside us.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~没想到Brian居然没和我们一起战斗。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Life wouldn't be worth living if we didn't to fight to survive. Ain't that right Jim?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~如果生存不需要战斗，生命就毫无价值。不是吗，Jim？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Jonathan. We got work to do here.
~z~Shit, Bill. I don't know where my head is right now. I been feeling weird.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Bill。我现在都摸不着头脑。实在是太怪了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Too right, man. Guy like you shouldn't waste his time with all that shit.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~太对了，兄弟。你这种人就不该在娘们身上浪费时间。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~or back in the lockup with you!
~z~You set us up - you've always wanted to be the one -
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你陷害我们。你一直觊觎权位，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Klebitz, man. What the fuck? What the fuck?
~z~Okay, Bill, you think you're so tough. How about we light a fucking fire. Come on!
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好了，Bill，你觉得你那么牛逼，要么我们来比一比？走起！

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Didn't particularly enjoy combat when I was in the marines, Johnny.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我在海军陆战队的时候就不太喜欢战斗，Johnny。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~since you two were both so vocal in your support of this deal.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~既然你俩都极力主张进行交易，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Not gonna waste my time with that crap. I got the brothers. All the hole I need at the house, man. Yeah!
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~跟女人浪费什么时间啊。老子有弟兄在，会所又有公交车。耶！

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Brian, man, what the fuck were you and Billy doing while those Triads jumped on me and Jim?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Brian，兄弟，我跟Jim被三合会袭击的时候你跟Billy在干嘛？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You just love sniffing out an argument, Billy boy. Enjoy the ride for a minute. Mellow out.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你就喜欢没事找事，Billy仔。先享受骑行吧，放松一下。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Chad's on the phone about the meeting.
~z~Let us find these men and get it over with. Follow me, my brothers.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~找到那伙人，解决他们。跟我来，兄弟们。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You're gonna have to take over the chapter presidency, Johnny. Only thing for it.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~必须由你接任分会会长了，Johnny。别无他选。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Important question, Brian. What happened there? Billy said these Triads were ready to deal.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~很重要的问题，Brian。当时怎么了？Billy不是说三合会准备好交易了吗。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You got lucky back there, man. Good race.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你的运气不错，兄弟。真是厉害。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~given the fact that we can't even stop fighting amongst ourselves!
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~更何况我们失落帮内部都还是剑拔弩张！

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~we should make the slopes pay us back.
~z~I know, because they did the same to me,
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我很清楚，因为他们就是这么对我的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Cops are poking round, Bill. We should chill out.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~条子正在调查，Bill。我们该避避风头。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~No I didn't. He nearly got me fucking killed.
~z~You trying to get yourself killed, Johnny?
~z~Well, Bill. I may have beat you, but you're still the fucking man in my book.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，Bill。也许我是赢了，但你还是我眼中最牛逼的人。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Maybe if you don't got anyone to look after, Johnny.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~可能是因为你没有需要牵挂的人吧，Johnny。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~When people hear about Billy going down, there's gonna be more pressure on us than ever.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~等别人知道Billy进去了，我们面对的压力还会更大。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Sure she did. Probably ran good before you touched her. Get out my face, Brian.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~当然了，你碰之前估计是好好的。滚蛋吧，Brian。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, man. We got to have a meet for all the brothers when we get back. Tell 'em what happened.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，老兄。回去后我们要召集所有弟兄开个会。告诉他们情况。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Look normally I'd be down for that,
~z~We still got shit to deal with here, Johnny.
~z~Brian, man. Shit's fucked. Billy's been taken down. Where are you?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Brian，兄弟，全都完了。Billy被抓走了。你在哪儿？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I'm surprised Brian's got balls enough to leave the house.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~没想到Brian居然敢走出会所大门。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~It was a pleasure beating you gentlemen.
~z~They got word out all over town.
~z~Sure as shit don't like it now.
~z~Look man we can do business or go to war.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~听着，老兄，我们可以谈生意，也可以直接干。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You're not as big as those days when you hit the 'roids either, William.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你的块头也不如打类固醇那会儿大了，William。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~And looking for a fight, is the wrong thing to do right now
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~而动用武力，不是现在该做的事，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I'd never talk to a pig. But there's a lesson to be learned, alright.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我不可能告密的。但的确要记住他的教训。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Tell me if I'm wrong, but you know more about this deal than you're letting on?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我错了你直说，但关于这次交易你是不是留了一手？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Did you get jealous and wish that Billy was fucking you instead? You'd like that wouldn't you, you fat little bitch?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你是不是吃醋了，希望被Billy操的人是你？这样你就高兴了是吧，死胖子？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Looks like they were prepared for this, Johnny.
~z~Great to see you guys. Shame Billy couldn't make it.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~很高兴见到你们，可惜Billy没能来到这里。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~He's gonna have plenty of time to think about his anger on the inside.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~进去以后他有的是时间生气。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Now let's find out what Brian's got to say.
~z~Well, Billy says we're doing it. So get doing it.
~z~Billy, I just don't see how we have a choice man.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Billy，我们现在根本就没得选，兄弟。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You keep talking like that - you are dead, my little friend.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~再说这种话，你就死定了，小朋友。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Let's see what Brian's got to say for himself.
~z~Yeah. Maybe he's starting to calm down.
~z~It's like being made Captain of a sinkin' ship. What am I gonna do?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~感觉就像是撞上冰山后被任命成船长了。我要做什么？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Look I just think that given this war we're back into with the Angels of Death,
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~听着，考虑到我们又和死亡天使开战了，

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Billy's inside and Jim's gone for good. You're a real lucky charm, buddy.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Billy进去了，Jim人没了。你的运气真好，伙计。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You ratted him out! You ratted him out!
~z~and they told me you ratted us out.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~他们都告诉我你出卖我们了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~We'll either end up dead in the ground,
~z~You haven't been talking have you? Don't go forgetting what happened when Horse sang his little ditty.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~该不会是你在告密吧？别忘了Horse想要告密的时候发生了什么。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I ain't going back there. I'd rather be dead.
~z~They sure as hell weren't covering us.
~z~Follow me, brothers. They're somewhere in here.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~跟我来，兄弟们。他们就在这里。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Jim. You're just a font of information, aren't you?
~z~and given the fact that one or possibly two government agencies
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~现在还有可能被一两个政府探员

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Well, why'd he bring me into it?
~z~Fine, okay. I'm just hoping my brothers didn't send me into an ambush.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~行，好。我只是希望不是有兄弟设局陷害我。
~z~妈的，真厉害啊，长官。太厉害了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Klebitz, man, what the fuck? What happened back there?
~z~Didn't think you guys were going to make it.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~没想到你们居然能来到这里。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I'm surprised Billy agreed to this. It's the first smart move he's made since gettin' out of rehab.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~没想到Billy居然同意了。这是他从戒毒所出来后的第一个明智之举。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You're gonna stick by your brothers. We got to pull together now.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你要和弟兄们站在一起。现在我们必须上下一心。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You know who I'm looking for. Where's Ashley?
~z~Fuck 'em, man. The two of us are chapter enough and Terry 'n' Clay will back you up when you need it.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~去他妈的，兄弟。光靠我们两个人都是分部了，而且Terry和Clay也会在需要的时候支援你。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I just think that getting rid of that stuff now is the right thing to do.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我只是觉得现在脱手那批货是明智之举。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Alright brothers. They're somewhere in here. Follow me.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好了，兄弟们。他们就在这里。跟我来。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You two want us to end up all dead?
~z~You love sniffing out a deal, don't you Johnny?
~z~Shit, man. There must be some weird gremlins fucking with my machine. She ran smooth earlier.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，兄弟，肯定是有小妖怪搞了我的摩托，之前还好好的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Nothing like a firefight to make the blood boil, eh Jim?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~枪战实在是让人血脉偾张啊，Jim。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~How many of these Triads are there?
~z~I don't prove shit to you and I didn't talk to no one.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我证明你妈呢，我也没去哪里告发。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~The Deadbeats told them we got it and they want it back.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~死妈天使说货在我们手里，中国人现在想要回去。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~He ain't gone, Brian, he's gone to prison.
~z~Billy doesn't have any beef, he's not trucking any bad shit with me.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Billy又没犯罪，他跟我身上没带什么坏东西。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Billy fucked Ashley, man. I watched them.
~z~We will take the product and your lives!
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们要拿走货，还有你们的性命！

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You do not want to push me. No, you do not.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~你不会想惹毛我的。真的，不会想的。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~We're gonna have to fight our way outta here.
~z~I have a choice - I'm free. I'm not a slave.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~当然能选。我有我的自由，不是奴隶。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Not if I got anything to say on it. Not if Billy hears about this.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~我反对的话就不可能。Billy知道了的话就不可能。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Brought it into Liberty on a ship called the Platypus a few weeks back.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~几周前用Platypus号货轮运进自由城的。
~z~大家都是兄弟，老兄。失落帮的兄弟。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Yeah. I'm real keen to tell the brothers what went down.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~好，我正好想跟弟兄们说明下情况。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~What? What are you and your boy here going to be doing?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~什么？那你和你的小弟来干什么？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~but there's other parts that are a lot bigger now I'm off the drugs. Just ask Ashley.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~但我停药以后也有变得巨大的地方，你去问Ashley吧。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~We got more important things to think about. Without Billy we got no leader.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~还有更重要的事情要考虑。Billy不在我们就群龙无首了。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna call Terry and the rest of 'em. Set up a meet.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~I'm gonna call Terry and the rest of 'em. Set up a meet.

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Getting out ain't gonna be easy. Where's fuckin' Bill?
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~要想逃出这里可不容易。Bill他妈人呢？

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~Yeah and since you've fucking been strung out on this shit
~z~Jim, dude. I'm happy to have you next to me on this run.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~Jim，老兄。很高兴这次陪我的人是你。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~A new power is rising. You shall see.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~新的力量正在崛起。等着瞧吧。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~You two are going to be the ones to hand over the brown to the slopes.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~把货交给这帮猴子的活就由你俩负责。

E1B6AUD.original: ~z~And tell Chad I'm sober as can be over here.
~z~He set us up and he called the cops.
E1B6AUD.translated: ~z~他给我们设下圈套，然后报警了。
